import React from 'react'
import SingleAnswerView from './SingleAnswerView'

export default function SingleAnswers(props) {

    return (
        <>
            <section className="flex flex-col w-[80%] overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-visible gap-2 flex-nowrap items-center h-[300px]">
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 1" name="answer1" update={props.update} value={props.a1Val} />
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 2" name="answer2" value={props.a2Val} />
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 3 (optional)" name="answer3" update={props.update} value={props.a3Val} />
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 4 (optional)" name="answer4" update={props.update} value={props.a4Val} />
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 5 (optional)" name="answer5" update={props.update} value={props.a5Val} />
                <SingleAnswerView placeholder="Answer 6 (optional)" name="answer6" update={props.update} value={props.a6Val} />
            </section> 
        </>
    )
}
